  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Social media content manager",
  "description": "<p>We are looking for a creative and motivated <strong>Social Media Manager / Content Creator</strong> to manage our company’s social media presence, create engaging content, and help generate leads for our renovation business.</p><p>You will be responsible for filming, editing, and posting short-form videos, managing social media accounts, and growing our brand online.</p><h2><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h2><h3><strong>Social Media Management</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Manage and grow Instagram, TikTok, Facebook, and LinkedIn accounts</p></li><li><p>Plan and execute content calendars</p></li><li><p>Write captions, hashtags, and post descriptions</p></li><li><p>Engage with followers and respond to comments and inquiries</p></li><li><p>Track performance and provide monthly reports</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Content Creation</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Film renovation site progress, before/after transformations, and client testimonials</p></li><li><p>Edit videos for TikTok, Instagram Reels, and YouTube Shorts</p></li><li><p>Add subtitles, music, branding, and visual effects</p></li><li><p>Create graphics and social media posts using Canva or Adobe tools</p></li></ul><h3><strong>Marketing Support</strong></h3><ul><li><p>Assist in marketing campaigns and promotions</p></li><li><p>Suggest content ideas to generate leads and brand awareness</p></li><li><p>Work with sales team to convert inquiries into leads</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Requirements</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Experience managing social media accounts for brands or businesses</p></li><li><p>Skilled in video editing tools (CapCut, Adobe Premiere Pro, DaVinci Resolve, etc.)</p></li><li><p>Familiar with TikTok and Instagram trends and algorithms</p></li><li><p>Creative mindset with good storytelling skills</p></li><li><p>Basic understanding of marketing and lead generation</p></li><li><p>Portfolio or sample videos required</p></li></ul><h2><strong>Preferred Skills (Bonus)</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Experience in renovation, real estate, or construction content</p></li><li><p>Copywriting and basic marketing funnel knowledge</p></li><li><p>Running social media ads (Meta / TikTok Ads)</p></li><li><p>Comfortable speaking on camera</p></li></ul><h2><strong>What We Offer</strong></h2><ul><li><p>Competitive salary based on experience</p></li><li><p>Flexible working arrangements (remote / hybrid)</p></li><li><p>Opportunity to grow with a fast-growing renovation company</p></li><li><p>Performance-based bonuses for lead generation</p></li></ul>",
