    "description": "<p>Commercial / Residential Construction firm since 2007</p>\n<p>Mission:</p>\n<p>Reno Bee aims to offer its clients exceptional construction and renovation services. Our core purpose is to create timeless, futuristic spaces that are both modern and functional.</p>\n<p>Vision:</p>\n<p>By offering cutting edge techniques and providing creative, user-centric innovations that will benefit both the client and the community at large, we hope to become the acknowledged leader in renovation and building works.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Service provided :</p>\n<p>-Interior designing&nbsp;</p>\n<p>-Carpentry frabrication</p>\n<p>-Electrical works</p>\n<p>-Painting</p>\n<p>-Partition</p>\n<p>-Reinstatement&nbsp;</p>\n<p>-A&amp;A / Building works</p>\n<p><br></p>",
